==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[hydrochloric]] [[acid]]'''
#{{chemistry}} A [[strong]] acid made by [[dissolving]] the [[gas]], [[hydrogen]] [[chloride]], in [[water]]. It [[react]]s with [[alkali]]s, [[base]]s and many [[metal]]s to form chlorides; it has many [[industrial]] [[application]]s'

====Synonyms====
*[[E507]] when used as an [[acidity regulator]]
*[[muriatic acid]]

